   276→            <p>
   277→                Rotating the N-th roots of unity by angle φ and projecting them onto the real axis yields N points.
   278→                The polynomial with these projections as roots, when scaled by 2<sup>N-1</sup>, equals the N-th Chebyshev
   279→                polynomial of the first kind plus a constant that depends on φ.
   280→            </p>
