   466→                Read the <a href="./paper/chebyshev_circles.pdf">research paper</a> for traditional mathematical exposition,
   467→                explore the <a href="./blueprint/">Blueprint</a> for an interactive map of the formalization,
   468→                check the <a href="./docs/">API Documentation</a> for detailed proofs, or view the
   469→                <a href="./graph/">Dependency Graph</a> to understand the proof structure.
   470→            </p>
